name: deep moon
description:
As I was flying in the sky, I felt the coldness of the night on my skin
I saw something fall into the sea
It goes deeper as time goes on, but its radiance never ends
I couldn't tell if it was the light of the moon falling into the sea or the moon itself
I dived into the sea to save the moon
No matter how deep I went, the Moon was always ahead of me
I chased
I chased
